      • setAssociationAttr

        public void setAssociationAttr(java.lang.String value)
        Injected, required. Name of attribute to "split" queueItems on. If sequential values of this attribute are the same, the subsequent rows will be added as a sub-queueItem to the most recently created main queueItem.
        Parameters:
        {String} - association attribute name.

        protected void loadPropertiesMap(java.lang.String[] csvLine,
                                 int rowNum)
        CSV with associations implementation of loadPropertiesMap. The method will call the parent implementation to ensure the properties map is fully loaded, before ensuring the associationAttr column is defined in the propertyColumn values. If it's not, the method will throw a fatal exception since this populator is being used incorrectly.
